  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went at, in '35.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anthropogeography.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two, myself and another girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my parents and my sister and her husband, they wanted me to study dentistry, because that was regarded as a good profession for the future.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the [? systematology ?] academy, there was an entrance exam.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I wrote that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was, among the questions, there was, why do you want to be a dentist?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wrote down, because my family forces me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on the board later was the result of the exams.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was, next to my name, a sentence that say, don't support forced labor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got my way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There has been a ripe anti-Semitism at the university.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, our indexes-- that is, books where all the professors had to sign that you made it-- have been stamped in different colors.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Green, green was for the non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And lilac stamps have been for the Jewish students, so that if you gave your index to the teacher or to the professor to--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He immediately knew that you were a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not my results, but in many cases, it did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've seen girls thrown out of the window from the first floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was early '39.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I also have been during the so-called student strike, where the Jewish students have striked and didn't go to university at all.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They stayed in this Jewish hostel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Jewish businesses, like bakeries and butchers, they sent into the house-- into this academic house, into the hostel-- food for the striking students.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Vera's husband was a revisionist and very active.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I haven't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
